name: Elements-js13-2014
tagline: Capture the flag, with jet packs!
body:
### Welcome to my JS13K 2014 game

It is a javascript game under 13kb (when zipped).
The theme this year is "4 elements: ground, water, fire, air"

Use space to fire the jetpack, left and right arrows to move.

Enjoy,
 @iftahh
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
